&lt;h2&gt;Our Mission&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;To disseminate information to parents via news blasts, newsletters and our website;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;To foster community within our school through various family and social events;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;To raise funds for programs to augment the school&amp;#39;s curriculum.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are many opportunities to get involved in the PTO; from volunteering a half hour of your time at an event, to chairing a committee, to serving on the PTO Board. All are welcome and no experience is necessary!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remember: &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Those who can, do...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; those who can do more, volunteer!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

